SelendisAdeptHero.Description:
Adept form of Selendis.

Can attack the ground and air.
SelendisAdeptHero.Name: Selendis

SelendisMothershipHero.Description:
Selendis commanding the "Purifier". An elegant, brave and honored Templar. As the high executor of the Golden Armada, Selendis possesses every honorable traits of a templar.

Can attack ground and air units.
SelendisMothershipHero.Name: Selendis

AssimilatorSelendis.Description: Warped in over a Vespene Geyser to allow harvesting of vespene gas.
AssimilatorSelendis.Name: Orbital Assimilator

CyberneticsCoreSelendis.Description: Provide weapon and armor upgrades for Protoss air units.
CyberneticsCoreSelendis.Name: Cybernetics Core

FleetBeaconSelendis.Description:
Tech structure for the Golden Armada.

Enables:
- Star of Radiance
- Meteorite of Star
FleetBeaconSelendis.Name: Fleet Beacon

ForgeSelendis.Description:
Provide upgrades for Protoss ground units and structures, as well as upgrades for Selendis.

Enables:
- Phase Photon Cannons
ForgeSelendis.Name: Forge

GatewaySelendis.Description:
Tech structure for basic Protoss ground units.

Enables:
- War Tuner
- High Chanter
GatewaySelendis.Name: Gateway

PhotonCannonSelendis.Description:
Main defensive structure.

Can attack ground and air units.
Detector
PhotonCannonSelendis.Name: Phase Photon Cannon

RoboticsBaySelendis.Description:
Tech structure for the Protoss war machines.

Enables:
- Sacred Colossus
RoboticsBaySelendis.Name: Robotics Bay

SelendisPunishArchon.Description: Powerful psionic attacker. The Wrath Archon can deal devastating damage to enemy units through melee attacks.**Can attack ground and air units**
SelendisPunishArchon.Name: Wrath Archon

SelendisTunerZealot.Description:
Main combat unit. War Tuner can use Slash and Battle Rage in zealot form.

Can attack ground units.
SelendisTunerZealot.Name: War Tuner

SelendisHighIntonater.Description: Potent psionic master. Can use Mournful Prayer to protect allied units and Covenant Fulfilled to deal massive damage.**Can attack ground units**
SelendisHighIntonater.Name: High Chanter

SelendisTunerAdept.Description:
Main combat unit. Can use Psionic Resonance to transform into a Zealot.

Can attack ground and air units.
SelendisTunerAdept.Name: War Tuner

TunerAdeptPhaseShift.Description: War Tuner switches to melee form, leaving a psionic phantom in place and jumping to the target unit. Psionic phantom lasts 15 seconds. Teleport back to phantom's position and restore all status after the time ends or it dies in melee form.
TunerAdeptPhaseShift.Name: Psionic Projection

SelendisProbe.Description: Basic worker unit. Flying Probe used by Protoss for expansion in distant sectors. Can gather resources and warp into Protoss structures.**Can attack ground units**
SelendisProbe.Name: Nexus Legate

SelendisProbeObserver.Description: Basic worker unit. Flying Probe used by Protoss for expansion in distant sectors. Provides power field and detection in its matrix form. Can also be used to gather resources continuously.**Can attack ground units**
SelendisProbeObserver.Name: Nexus Legate

SelendisNexus.Description:
Primary structure. Can produce workers. Can provide power field for nearby structures.

The Celestial Nexus can be attached with a warp platform or warp array to continuously warp in Protoss forces and put them on standby, responding to expedition and recall orders which can be activated from the top panel.

Enables:
- Nexus Legate
SelendisNexus.Name: Celestial Nexus

TemplarArchiveSelendis.Description:
Tech structure for the High Templars.

Enables:
- Wrath Archon
TemplarArchiveSelendis.Name: Templar Archive

StargateSelendis.Description:
Tech structure for basic Protoss air units.

Enables:
-Wings of Stardust
-Echoes of Galaxy
StargateSelendis.Name: Stargate

SelendisCarrier.Description: Capital ship. Builds and launches more Interceptors that attack enemy targets, can also charges up a main cannon to deal even more damage.**Can attack ground and air units**
SelendisCarrier.Name: Meteorite of Star

SelendisVoidRay.Description:
Surgical strike craft. Can use Radiant Prism to gradually increase its stats while attacking.

Can attack ground and air units.
SelendisVoidRay.Name: Star of Radiance

SelendisOracle.Description:
Flying Caster. Can continuously weaken targeted enemy unit, and ultimately deal heavy damage to it.**Can attack ground units**
Detector
SelendisOracle.Name: Echoes of Galaxy

SelendisPhoenix.Description: Air superiority starfighter. Can use Countless Sparks and Starlight to deal with large amounts of enemy air units.**Can attack air units**
SelendisPhoenix.Name: Wings of Stardust

SelendisColossus.Description: Battle strider with a powerful area attack. Can walk up and down cliffs. Attacks can track enemy units to deal heavy area damage and can also stop their advance.**Can attack ground units**
SelendisColossus.Name: Sacred Colossus

SelendisZealotHero.Description: Zealot form of Selendis.**Can attack the ground**
SelendisZealotHero.Name: Selendis
